{"tid":1946802,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】「黃蜂女」伊雲祖蓮莉莉承認失言公開道歉","createTime":"2020-03-28T00:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T04:53:06.000Z","uid":41343,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6e63e2bc95b931e72b00cf8bc2528b2ef75230b3","tid":1946802,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:21:16.000Z","msg":"《蟻俠》（Ant-Man）女主角「黃蜂女」伊雲祖蓮莉莉（Evangeline Lilly）日前在IG表示在武漢肺炎疫情下，仍然如常帶孩子到體操營，又指自己重視自由過於生命，不負責任的言論被網友鬧爆，就連《權力遊戲》（Game of Thrones）英國女星Sophie Turner亦睇唔過眼，拍片爆粗暗寸她是白痴，伊雲祖蓮昨日終於跪低承認失言及向粉絲道歉。<br />\n<br />\n伊雲祖蓮上載孩子在家玩大富翁的照片，留言：「儘管我對社會經濟和政治後果感到非常不安，但請你們知道我亦做好社交隔離和與家人留在家中。我想對我之前留言的漠視態度真誠道歉，武漢肺炎令世界帶來痛苦和恐懼，全世界都在尋求方法去停止這個真正的威脅，我的沉默傳遞了一個輕蔑、傲慢和難解的訊息。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200327/RCKLTGVSTDPFEYWRYUFBKYTWBM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200327%2FRCKLTGVSTDPFEYWRYUFBKYTWBM%2F&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=b19ea343\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200327%2FRCKLTGVSTDPFEYWRYUFBKYTWBM%2F&h=532c5504\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200327/RCKLTGVSTDPFEYWRYUFBKYTWBM/</a>"},{"pid":"16e458a2bef54d39ffcc1a16d0d3bd54202c6a33","tid":1946802,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:13:33.000Z","msg":"有冇Sophie tuner條片睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a91d17963ca3e512391b943a32db91fadd969f9","tid":1946802,"uid":322685,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"16e458a2bef54d39ffcc1a16d0d3bd54202c6a33","tid":1946802,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:13:33.000Z","msg":"有冇Sophie tuner條片睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:20:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qucGhUVrlCg\" data-sr-url=\"https: